<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Reflective Questions</title>
<style>
body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 40px; max-width: 900px; margin: auto; }
ul { line-height: 1.6; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Reflective Question Bank</h1>

<ul>
<li>What stands out most for you?</li>
<li>If you described this in a few lines, what would you say?</li>
<li>What was happening inside for you?</li>
<li>What did you notice in your body or thoughts?</li>
<li>What sense were you making of it?</li>
<li>Which values felt present or challenged?</li>
<li>What might support you now?</li>
<li>What would you like to take into supervision?</li>
</ul>

</body>
</html>
